    </div>
</div>

<!-- About Section -->
<section class="bg-success py-5" style="background-color: #000000;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center py-5">
            <div class="col-md-8 text-white">
                <h1 style="color: #bb9d2b;">About PayTag</h1>
                <p>
                    At <strong>PayTag</strong>, we're transforming how brands connect with people through the power of social media. Our platform creates a win-win loop where <strong>shoppers and influencers earn real cashback</strong> by tagging us in Instagram stories after purchasing products from partnered brands.
                    <br><br>
                    We empower everyday users, content creators, and micro-influencers to turn their social reach into rewards—<em>no huge follower count needed</em>. Brands gain authentic, user-generated promotion, while we handle the tech, tracking, and payouts behind the scenes.
                    <br><br>
                    From discovery to rewards, we make shopping more rewarding, marketing more authentic, and growth more accessible. Welcome to the new way of social selling.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="~/img/about-hero.svg" alt="PayTag Hero" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

